*Shadow Cat and Snow Tech dislodge from their tangle of limbs. Shadow Cat 
jumps to her feet, embarrased that Snow Tech would humiluate her this way*

" God you can be SO dumb Snow Tech. You do have brakes, don't you?"

* She then looked at prowl how had just then spoken, and nodded*

" Yeah, old friends. We where best buds back on the home planet, but we had 
to leave on a scouting mission and where gone for a long period of time, 
when we got back, IR was gone. Since we couldn't ask the mission control 
unit where she went, we broke into their computer system and tracked her to 
this sector. It was then all up to chance to find out where she was."

*She turns her head to Iron Raptor and speaks*

" So, i've seen you've changed since we've last met. Er... It's, um, 
different, thats for shure!"

* She smiles and goes to give Ir a hug, for old times sake, triping over 
Snow Tech, who had not risen off the ground since he fell, but layed their 
and watched every-one from his ground view.*

"SNOW TECH! YOU ASS!"

* Snow Tech smiles and gets to his feet, dusting himself off and walks over 
to IR, grabing her arm, causing the little 'un to lose his sence of balance. 
the little 'un twists out of ir's grasp and flies to Prowl, curious to what 
this thing was. Meanwhile, Snow Tech turns to Prowl*

" Hi, I'm Iron's Lover. 'Scuse me while i go make mad, pattinote love to 
her!"
